			Profile
			
			


Introduce:
ProfessorZhiyuWanghasbeenengagedintheDepartmentofMaterialsScienceandEngineeringatZheiangUniversitySince1992.HeobtainedhisPh.DinMaterialsSciencefromthesameUniversityin1999.In2004,hehasbeenashorttimeVisitingResearcheratthePhotonCraftProject,ICORP,JSTinJapan.In2007,hegothiscurrentprofessionaltitleofProfessor.Heisthecoordinatorofmanynationalprojectsandtheauthorofmorethan120scientificpapers(morethan90onISIjournals).Healsohas22patents.
Hismainresearchinterestsincludeï¼š1)toinvolveinconstructionongraduateprogramsandsubjectsofstudyinthematerialsphysicsandchemistryofnanofunctionalmaterialsandhybridorganic-inorganicmaterials,2)tostudyhybridorganic-inorganicphotonicmaterials(solidtunablelasermedia,luminescencematerialsandnonlinearopticalmaterials);photonicglasses;photoniccrystals;opticalspectroscopy;surfaceandinterfaceofmaterials;novelpropertiesinnanostructures;anddevice-relatedmaterialproblems,3)todevelopapplicationtechnologyfornewfunctionalcompositebuildingmaterials,andcontributetotheindustrialprosperitythroughcollaborationwithcompanies.
